--[[
    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║           SECRET CHAT  v2.0              ║
    ║  Peer-to-peer • Handshake-verified       ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════╝

    CONTROLS
    ─────────────────────────────────────────
    [Right Shift]   Toggle window open/closed
    [Enter]         Send message
    Drag title bar  Reposition window

    HOW IT WORKS
    ─────────────────────────────────────────
    Every user running this script broadcasts a hidden handshake
    tag through Roblox chat. Other script users intercept it and
    mark each other as "verified". Secret messages are similarly
    prefixed, hidden from Roblox's native chat, and shown only
    inside this window.

    To isolate your own group, change SCRIPT_KEY below.
    Both users must share the exact same key to communicate.
]]

